title: 1 bedroom apartment available!
posting_body: ['Parkridge Way Apartments is nestled in a quiet and peaceful New Hope neighborhood.', 'Mature trees, parks with in walking distance, restaurants, grocery, YMCA within blocks, and down the street from Downtown Robbinsdale or New Hope Community Center.', 'Easy access to either Hwy 169 or Hwy 100.', "Can't beat New Hope!", 'The one bedroom apartment we have available is a second floor Aquilla floor plan at 750sq ft.', 'This unit has wonderful caramel colored cabinets that reach the ceiling-so plenty of cabinet space.', 'Large balcony will accommodate a table with a couple chairs and even a lounge chair!', 'Available August 10th, this unit is renting for $1,050.00 a month.', 'Community Amenities', '• Controlled Access Entry', 'On-site Professional Management', '• Wi-fi-computer room', '• Garage parking and off street parking', '• Dog run and pet stations throughout the property', '• Fitness Center', '• Indoor Swimming Pool and spa', '• Community room', '• On-site Professional Management', 'Apartment Amenities', '• Air Conditioning', '• Dishwasher', '• Heat Included in Rent', '• Spacious Balconies/Patios', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed', '• Comments: Cats and dogs welcome', '• Restrictions: Breed Restrictions may apply']
